  {"id": "1380899115860230205", "type": 0, "content": "## Useful Links\n\n### [Wiki (Github)](https://github.com/alicia86/SW_ForgottenOnes/wiki)\n\n### [Chapter Logs](https://galacticcampaigns.com/logs?c=forgotten_ones)\n\n### [Macro List](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQnEg5o0rLw1_O6zXA4QNUeQvt4A0uvVXPMtEhwAX4h9pUbbHAXXEHkYKkmeVstit7Z15An1RYQGbRX/pubhtml?gid=1566290861&single=true)", "channel_id": "1380898627131801700", "author": {"id": "208916238661844993", "username": "aliciagd", "avatar": "d7832f2cac5df42d164b81e35de34f09", "bot": false}, "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": {"id": null, "name": "📌"}, "count": 1}], "timestamp": "2025-06-07T13:20:05.086000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-14T19:03:15.686000+00:00", "flags": 4, "thread": null, "position": 0, "userName": "aliciagd"},
